      "weather": "Fine",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KAELIX STORM (3) is progressing well scoring last time out (25.05) at Warrnambool and bringing up his 4th career win. Hard to go past form here, unbeaten in two starts. Has won two of two starts from this draw. Looks the testing material. LEKTRA BETA (8) is better than last start when fifth (25.91) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool over 450m. Form here sound including four wins. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Expected to give a good account. DASH EXPRESS (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Paw Farok (27.47) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Must be included in calculations. ASTON HERCULES (2) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
